        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've spent way too many Sunday nights staring at spreadsheets, trying to figure out who's available on Tuesday morning and whether I already gave Jamie three shifts this week. If you manage a team — whether it's a café, a farm attraction, a retail store, or a warehouse — you know the drill. Scheduling eats time you don't have.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://try.shiftie.co/t05s3i9e144c"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That's why ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Shiftie",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " caught my attention. It's a UK-built staff scheduling platform that handles rota creation, availability, leave requests, timesheets, and team messaging — all in one place. No clunky spreadsheets. No WhatsApp chaos. Just a clean system that actually works.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Below are seven tips and best practices for getting the most out of Shiftie from day one.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. Build Your First Rota in Under 10 Minutes",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The biggest barrier to adopting any new tool is the setup. Shiftie removes that friction completely. When you log in for the first time, the onboarding walks you through adding employees, setting locations, and publishing your first rota.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's what I recommend:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Import your team list first.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Add names, roles, and contact details. Shiftie lets you invite employees to the app so they can manage their own availability — which saves you a ton of back-and-forth.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Set your venue or venues.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " If you run multiple locations (a restaurant with two branches, for example), Shiftie handles multi-venue scheduling natively. No workarounds needed.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Drag and drop to build shifts.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " The scheduling interface is visual and fast. You grab a shift block, drop it onto a day, assign a person, and move on. What used to take an hour on Excel takes ten minutes.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-shiftie"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you want a detailed walkthrough, check our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "step-by-step guide on how to use Shiftie",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. Let Employees Manage Their Own Availability",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is where Shiftie really shines compared to manual scheduling. Instead of texting each person to ask when they can work, you let the platform handle it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Employees log into the Shiftie app and set their availability preferences. When you build a rota, you can see at a glance who's free, who's on leave, and who's already maxed out on hours. No guesswork.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pro tip:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Set a policy early. Tell your team to update availability at least two weeks out. Once that habit clicks, scheduling becomes almost automatic.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This single feature eliminates the most common scheduling headaches: double-booking, understaffing, and the endless \"can you cover?\" messages.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. Use the Leave Management System (Instead of Email Chains)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've seen teams track vacation requests in shared Google Sheets, Outlook calendars, even paper forms pinned to a breakroom wall. Every one of those systems has the same flaw: information gets lost.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Shiftie's built-in leave management keeps everything centralized. Employees submit requests through the app. Managers approve or decline with one click. Approved leave automatically shows up on the rota, so you never accidentally schedule someone who's on holiday.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For small teams, this alone justifies the cost. For larger operations, it's a lifesaver — especially during peak seasons when every shift slot matters.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. Automate Timesheets and Cut Payroll Prep Time",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-shiftie"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Chasing down clock-in times is tedious. Shiftie includes a ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "time clock and timesheet feature",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " that tracks when employees start and end their shifts. The data rolls up into timesheets you can review before running payroll.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "No more asking \"what time did you leave on Thursday?\" The system knows.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For businesses that pay by the hour — hospitality, events, retail — this feature alone can save several hours per payroll cycle. It also creates a clean audit trail, which protects both you and your team.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
